# Frontend Rules

- Use App Router conventions and keep route components lean.
- Prefer shared UI and typed contracts from `packages/ui`, and `packages/types`.
- Validate public env vars before creating Supabase clients.
- Favor accessible semantic HTML, clear loading states, and readable Tailwind class groups.
- Add or update Vitest tests for component and contract changes.
- Keep Vercel compatibility in mind: no server-only code in client bundles.
